    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking for a new home for this awesome car! It\u2019s in really lovely shape and has been such a dependable companion for me. It drives smoothly and still looks great pulling into any driveway. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have! I\u2019m super easy to chat with, so please feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I\u2019d love to help you get behind the wheel! \u2728",
