    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This unit utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. The VANOS system has been recently recalibrated, and the rear subframe\u2014a known point of fatigue\u2014has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. Suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and 50/50 weight balance this chassis is celebrated for. While the exterior shows honest road wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are strong, pulling linearly to the 8,000 RPM redline without hesitation. A mechanically sound, analog performance machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 32500.0,
